            "abstract": "© The Author(s) 2018. Published by Oxford University Press.MODE-TASK, a novel and versatile software suite, comprises Principal Component Analysis, Multidimensional Scaling, and t-Distributed Stochastic Neighbor Embedding techniques using Molecular Dynamics trajectories. MODE-TASK also includes a Normal Mode Analysis tool based on Anisotropic Network Model so as to provide a variety of ways to analyse and compare large-scale motions of protein complexes for which long MD simulations are prohibitive. Beside the command line function, a GUI has been developed as a PyMOL plugin.",
